To install service:

sudo cp psm.server.service psm.worker.service psm.elasticsearch.service /lib/systemd/system
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl enable psm.server.service
sudo systemctl enable psm.worker.service
sudo systemctl enable psm.elasticsearch.service

To start/stop service:

sudo systemctl start psm.[server|worker|elasticsearch].service
sudo systemctl stop psm.[server|worker|elasticsearch].service
sudo systemctl restart psm.[server|worker|elasticsearch].service

To check status:

sudo systemctl status psm.[server|worker|elasticsearch].service
